text: Larry Kramer, the tireless author, playwright and LGBT activist, has died at 84. He was a firebrand to the end, which came Wednesday, May 27, when he died of pneumonia in Manhattan, where he lived with his husband, David Webster.  https://t.co/G9yAhHWerO https://t.co/Ql7f0K1Hnn
